},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 29:19","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":19,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 32:33","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":33,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 35:14–15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":14,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 44:4","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":4,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" ‘Obey me.’ "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Ch 36:15","book":"2Ch","chapter":36,"verse":15},{"label":"Jr 7:13","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":13},{"label":"Jr 7:25","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":25},{"label":"Jr 25:3","book":"Jer","chapter":25,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 26:5","book":"Jer","chapter":26,"verse":5},{"label":"Jr 29:19","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":19},{"label":"Jr 32:33","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":33},{"label":"Jr 35:14–15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 44:4","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit today, rising early and warning"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yet they would not obey or pay attention; each one followed the stubbornness of his evil heart. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 3:17","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:24","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 16:12","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" So I brought on them all the curses of this covenant, because they had not done what I commanded them to do.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 3:17","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":17},{"label":"Jr 7:24","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":24},{"label":"Jr 16:12","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" said to me, “A conspiracy has been discovered among the men of Judah "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 22:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":22,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 6:9","book":"Hos","chapter":6,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the residents of Jerusalem. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 22:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":22,"verse":25},{"label":"Hs 6:9","book":"Hos","chapter":6,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They have returned to the iniquities of their ancestors "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:39","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":39,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 9:2","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 65:7","book":"Isa","chapter":65,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" who refused to obey my words and have followed other gods to worship them. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 28:14","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 13:10","book":"Jer","chapter":13,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 35:15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":15,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" The house of Israel and the house of Judah broke my covenant I made with their ancestors."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 26:39","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":39},{"label":"Neh 9:2","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":2},{"label":"Is 65:7","book":"Isa","chapter":65,"verse":7},{"label":"Dt 28:14","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 13:10","book":"Jer","chapter":13,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 35:15","book":"Jer","chapter":35,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore, this is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says: I am about to bring on them disaster that they cannot escape. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 39:4–7","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 9:1–4","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" They will cry out to me, but I will not hear them. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 39:4–7","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":4},{"label":"Am 9:1–4","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then the cities of Judah and the residents of Jerusalem will go and cry out to the gods they have been burning incense to, but they certainly will not save them in their time of disaster. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:35","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 32:35","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":35}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Your gods are indeed as numerous as your cities, Judah, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:28","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the altars you have set up to Shame "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"= Baal"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 3:24","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 9:10","book":"Hos","chapter":9,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" —altars to burn incense to Baal —as numerous as the streets of Jerusalem."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 2:28","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":28},{"label":"Jr 3:24","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":24},{"label":"Hs 9:10","book":"Hos","chapter":9,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"= Baal"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“As for you, do not pray for these people. Do not raise up a cry or a prayer on their behalf, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:16","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 14:11","book":"Jer","chapter":14,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for I will not be listening when they call out to me at the time of their disaster."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 7:16","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":16},{"label":"Jr 14:11","book":"Jer","chapter":14,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What right does my beloved have"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" named you"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies who planted you "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:2","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:7","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:21","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" has decreed disaster against you, because of the disaster "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or evil"},{"kind":"text","text":" the house of Israel and the house of Judah brought on themselves when they angered me by burning incense to Baal.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 5:2","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":2},{"label":"Is 5:7","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 2:21","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or evil"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" informed me, so I knew."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"for I was like a docile "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or pet"},{"kind":"text","text":" lamb led to slaughter. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 44:11","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 44:22","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 53:7","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 12:3","book":"Jer","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 44:11","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":11},{"label":"Ps 44:22","book":"Psa","chapter":44,"verse":22},{"label":"Is 53:7","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 12:3","book":"Jer","chapter":12,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or pet"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But, "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies, who judges righteously,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, here is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says concerning the people of Anathoth "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 1:1","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 32:7–9","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" who intend to take your life. They warn, “Do not prophesy in the name of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 7:13","book":"Amo","chapter":7,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" or you will certainly die at our hand.” "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 1:1","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Jr 32:7–9","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":7},{"label":"Am 7:13","book":"Amo","chapter":7,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, this is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies says: “I am about to punish them. The young men will die by the sword; their sons and daughters will die by famine. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 7:16–17","book":"Amo","chapter":7,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Am 7:16–17","book":"Amo","chapter":7,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:11:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They will have no remnant, for I will bring disaster on the people of Anathoth "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:12","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the year of their punishment.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 23:12","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099441637}